My kwentong jeepney:
I was in Diliman and sumakay ako ng jeep na pa-Quezon Av. Umupo ako sa tabi ni Manong Driver and nagkwentuhan pa kame. Sobrang bangag ko from work, bumaba ako ng jeep without giving my bayad. Wondering why may barya sa pocket ko which is intended for the fare

As a working student, Christopher Olimpio sees the LRT Line 1 fare hike as unfair, especially for those covering students' expenses. He points out that the increase feels unreasonable compared to the modest 1-2 peso rise in jeepney fares.

THE TRANSPORTATION department should consider tapping local jeepney makers rather than importing public utility jeepneys under the government’s modernization plan to limit fare increases, a congressman said on Monday.
